{%- comment -%}
  URL for a media-gallery image_picker setting with a theme-asset fallback.

  Usage:
    {% render 'aico-image-src', image: settings.aico_x_image, fallback: 'x.jpg' %}

  Outputs the resolved gallery CDN URL (already locale-variant-aware — the
  settings hydrator picks the current storefront locale's image variant) when
  the setting resolves, else the legacy theme asset via asset_url — so an
  unset or dangling aico:// ref never breaks the page. Fallbacks are
  transitional: they go away one release after the asset files are deleted
  (M1 Phase D).
{%- endcomment -%}
{%- if image != blank -%}{{ image | image_url }}{%- else -%}{{ fallback | asset_url }}{%- endif -%}
